items.title: Samples field schema
items.description: Samples field schema generated by the CEDAR Template Editor 2.7.1

propertyDescriptions.Disease: If aplicable, Name of the disease in the study as described by the Human Disease Ontology [DOID](https://bioportal.bioontology.org/ontologies/DOID)
propertyDescriptions.Sample Provider: Company or laboratory that provided the sample (free text)
propertyDescriptions.Sample Origin: Biological structure the sample originates from as described by the Uber Anatomy Ontology [UBERON](https://bioportal.bioontology.org/ontologies/UBERON)
propertyDescriptions.Cell Type: Main Cell type present in the sample as described by the BRENDA Tissue and Enzyme Source Ontology [BTO](https://bioportal.bioontology.org/ontologies/BTO)
propertyDescriptions.Treatment Specify: Treatment applied in the study (free text)
propertyDescriptions.Cell Line: if aplicable, Cell Line Name as described by Cell Line Ontology [CLO](https://bioportal.bioontology.org/ontologies/CLO)
propertyDescriptions.Age (Value): Numeric quantity of time units from the Age (Unit) field
propertyDescriptions.Other Species: Fill in case you have selected Other as species
propertyDescriptions.Tumor Subtype: Morphological tumor type as described by the [SNOMED Clinical Terms ontology](https://bioportal.bioontology.org/ontologies/SNOMEDCT)
